        "id": 1000603
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-01-03T20:41:12Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "For shorter playlists (which I have to believe are the more typical) it\u0027ll be relatively accurate (and quick).  \n\nI think there are good arguments to be made either way here, but ultimately it depends on the user\u0027s specific specific playlists..",
